Package org.openpreservation.odf.xml

Enum Class OdfNamespaces

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<OdfNamespaces>
org.openpreservation.odf.xml.OdfNamespaces
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<OdfNamespaces>, java.lang.constant.Constable, Namespace
public enum OdfNamespaces extends Enum<OdfNamespaces> implements Namespace
Enum representing the XML namespaces used by ODF (OpenDocument Format). The enum implements the Namespace interface, so that it plays nicely with the XML classes in the ODF library. Each instance ties the namespace URI to a prefix and a description of the namespace. The instance names are the official prefix values in uppercase. Read the descriptions of each instance for more info.
